OL,3,CFormer mayor pleads not guilty to
OL,4,Cbribery and misconduct
OL,6,FA former mayor has pleaded not guilty
OL,7,Fto charges of bribery and misconduct.
OL,9,FJoe Anderson, 67, who was mayor of
OL,10,FLiverpool, entered not guilty pleas to
OL,11,Fbribery, misconduct in a public office
OL,12,Fand conspiracy to commit misconduct in
OL,13,Fa public office.
OL,15,FAnderson, who was Liverpool's elected
OL,16,Fmayor from 2012 to 2021, is alleged to
OL,17,Fhave sent or arranged to have sent
OL,18,F"threatening letters" to himself.
