OL,3,CFormer mayor pleads not guilty to
OL,4,Cbribery and misconduct
OL,6,FThe former Labour politician, of
OL,7,FKnotty Ash, Liverpool, is also accused
OL,8,Fof conspiring with his son, David
OL,9,FAnderson, and the council's former
OL,10,Fassistant director of highways and
OL,11,Fplanning, Andrew Barr, 51, to arrange
OL,12,Fspecial access in a manner to benefit
OL,13,FDavid Anderson and his company SSC.
OL,15,FBarr appeared alongside Anderson in
OL,16,Fthe dock, at Manchester Crown Court,
OL,17,Fand pleaded not guilty to conspiracy
OL,18,Fto commit misconduct in a public
OL,19,Foffice and accepting a bribe.
