OL,3,CFormer mayor pleads not guilty to
OL,4,Cbribery and misconduct
OL,6,FThey were charged as part of Operation
OL,7,FAloft, launched by Merseyside Police
OL,8,Fto look into the awarding of
OL,9,Fcommercial and business contracts from
OL,10,Fthe council between 2010 and 2020.
OL,12,FCo-defendants David Anderson, Derek
OL,13,FHatton, who was deputy council leader
OL,14,Fin the 1980s, and his wife, Sonjia
OL,15,FHatton, were not due to appear in
OL,16,Fcourt on Friday.
OL,18,FJudge Paul Lawton adjourned the case
OL,19,Funtil 5 April 2027 when the trial will
OL,20,Ftake place.
